{"tid":1168347,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《基本法》恐再失守！皇崗口岸2年後取消「兩地兩檢」涉違憲","createTime":"2019-05-23T15:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T11:14:13.000Z","uid":241093,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d633eccaf16ecde70a50073089c29bfa2caeb058","tid":1168347,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"繼高鐵西九站強推「一地兩檢」，打開《基本法》缺口後，隨時再有關口「失守」。據中共喉舌《文匯報》報道，深圳企圖借皇崗口岸重建，2021年停止貨運功能後，擬在口岸引入「兩地一檢」的客運過關模式，取消港深兩地口岸之間的緩衝區，兩地邊界將直接接合，兩地的兩套個人資料亦會合併在同一地點檢查。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">深圳市口岸辦昨回覆本港傳媒查詢時，強硬表明皇崗重建後，肯定不再實施現時的「兩地兩檢」。</span></span>不過有本港法律學者質疑，「兩地一檢」無論香港或內地境內實施，均違反《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190523/59632233?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F59632233%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhDQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=6a48ff5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F59632233%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=674c68bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190523/59632233?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港豬：淘寶係咪可以包郵？以後上多啲深圳食多啲元素先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img